39,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"我地要藍店翻身機會都無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8d44bd701e1fe0541a7e68362745d7f187f2c5","tid":2070449,"uid":139439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"唔想藍店死灰復撚？一人行多步"},{"pid":"4201411184e142191b340d9fc03a5048cfc4e55f","tid":2070449,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"489b79d0244c35bf4d067c29d4611e51e4355fa9","tid":2070449,"uid":139439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以參考下大眾點評同美團果啲咁？<br />\n雖然係大陸野但人地咁成功一定有佢原因<br />\n以前係支那intern用過係幾方便 <br />\n可以搜你附近/你要去既地方有咩優惠或者熱門店 <br />\n然後有得睇啲人評語再決定食咩<br />\n而加好多黃店app但就咁啲用家評語<br />\n衣 食 住 行包括哂<br />\n基本上依賴個app就可以安排你一日行程"},{"pid":"f5d7de2da75e65666d26534113c7b8264b8bab01","tid":2070449,"uid":139439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"而加黃圈初起好大問題係好多集中係食方面<br />\n其他方面反而難啲配對到商戶同客戶"},{"pid":"64c241194904f52323742129c4319ee6adbe53fe","tid":2070449,"uid":239035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"推 做實事"},{"pid":"d2cdbc42bd79b161302169c146a89a9d231b2eee","tid":2070449,"uid":307286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"push"}]}